DataElement.preferredName: FSFI 2 Past 4 Weeks Level Sexual Desire or Interest Score 5 Point Scale
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A person's stated rating in the past 4 weeks of their level (degree) of sexual desire or interest, using a 5 point Likert scale.

DataElementConcept.preferredName: Female Sexual Function Index Past 4 Weeks Level of Sexual Desire or Interest Score
DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: A 19-item self-report questionnaire designed to measure sexual function in women. ReferenceDocuments.name: Using PRO/HRQoL Measures
ReferenceDocuments.description: This data element is part of a full set of items that comprise a PRO/HRQoL measure. The full set must be used without any changes to the questions or value set in order to retain the validity and reliability associated with the measure. Changes may not be made to these documents. In cases where retaining the question set intact to preserve the validity and reliability are not as important as advancing the science, questions may be used individually or in combination with other measure questions.
